{
  "video_id": "B8j73TgzZDk",
  "title": "How to Speak Fluent English Without Hesitation?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 262.0,
      "end_time": 4114.0,
      "text": "- Hello, I'm Julian Northbrook from DoingEnglish.com."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4114.0,
      "end_time": 6697.0,
      "text": "(lively music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8805.0,
      "end_time": 13258.0,
      "text": "How to speak fluent English without hesitation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13258.0,
      "end_time": 14434.0,
      "text": "It's a good question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14434.0,
      "end_time": 16785.0,
      "text": "and it's one that many of you are asking."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 16785.0,
      "end_time": 19545.0,
      "text": "I've got two things to say on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19545.0,
      "end_time": 22211.0,
      "text": "The first is a little bit simpler."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22211.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "It might sound a little bit patronising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27162.0,
      "text": "but it's very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 27162.0,
      "end_time": 31324.0,
      "text": "The second is a little bit more complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31324.0,
      "end_time": 35249.0,
      "text": "It's a little bit deeper, but it's also very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35249.0,
      "end_time": 36966.0,
      "text": "But first things first."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 36966.0,
      "end_time": 38233.0,
      "text": "When people say to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38233.0,
      "end_time": 41311.0,
      "text": "I'm struggling to speak English well."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41311.0,
      "end_time": 43144.0,
      "text": "I'm not fluent in English."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43144.0,
      "end_time": 45080.0,
      "text": "I hesitate when I speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45080.0,
      "end_time": 49482.0,
      "text": "I can't respond to people quickly, automatically in English."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49482.0,
      "end_time": 52737.0,
      "text": "My first question for them is always"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 52737.0,
      "end_time": 54737.0,
      "text": "how much time and energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 56909.0,
      "end_time": 61025.0,
      "text": "are you putting in to learning the language?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61025.0,
      "end_time": 63691.0,
      "text": "Learning the English that you need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63691.0,
      "end_time": 66232.0,
      "text": "and then practising it to get good at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66232.0,
      "end_time": 68720.0,
      "text": "It's such an obvious thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68720.0,
      "end_time": 71177.0,
      "text": "but you'd be amazed at how many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71177.0,
      "end_time": 74860.0,
      "text": "actually really aren't doing much of anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74860.0,
      "end_time": 78564.0,
      "text": "You see, what happens is people have a conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78564.0,
      "end_time": 80862.0,
      "text": "in English with an overseas client,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80862.0,
      "end_time": 83235.0,
      "text": "somebody from their work, whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83235.0,
      "end_time": 86485.0,
      "text": "And they will completely screw that up."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88042.0,
      "end_time": 91345.0,
      "text": "They will misunderstand something, say something stupid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91345.0,
      "end_time": 93996.0,
      "text": "the whole thing will go horribly wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93996.0,
      "end_time": 96967.0,
      "text": "and they end up horribly embarrassed about the whole thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96967.0,
      "end_time": 99631.0,
      "text": "They go home, and they search on their computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99631.0,
      "end_time": 101160.0,
      "text": "how to improve my English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101160.0,
      "end_time": 104655.0,
      "text": "how to speak fluent English without hesitation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104655.0,
      "end_time": 107677.0,
      "text": "or whatever it is that they type in."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 107677.0,
      "end_time": 111809.0,
      "text": "And they are super motivated to improve their English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111809.0,
      "end_time": 113976.0,
      "text": "for about a day, two days."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115826.0,
      "end_time": 118999.0,
      "text": "And then, the embarrassment fades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118999.0,
      "end_time": 121464.0,
      "text": "they feel a bit better about the whole thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121464.0,
      "end_time": 125298.0,
      "text": "Time, as they say, is a great healer."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125298.0,
      "end_time": 127914.0,
      "text": "Then suddenly other things come up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127914.0,
      "end_time": 132084.0,
      "text": "work gets busy, there are good things to watch on TV,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132084.0,
      "end_time": 134301.0,
      "text": "beer to be drunk in the pub."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134301.0,
      "end_time": 136968.0,
      "text": "English gets pushed to one side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137873.0,
      "end_time": 139668.0,
      "text": "and never gets done."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139668.0,
      "end_time": 143296.0,
      "text": "Until of course, the next time they have a conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143296.0,
      "end_time": 145921.0,
      "text": "with an overseas client, or somebody from their work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145921.0,
      "end_time": 148698.0,
      "text": "or whoever it is that they speak English with."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 148698.0,
      "end_time": 151347.0,
      "text": "And once again, the whole thing goes horribly wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151347.0,
      "end_time": 154247.0,
      "text": "and they end up horribly embarrassed all over again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154247.0,
      "end_time": 157323.0,
      "text": "and repeat the same situation again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157323.0,
      "end_time": 159297.0,
      "text": "and again, and again."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 159297.0,
      "end_time": 161423.0,
      "text": "You don't need me to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161423.0,
      "end_time": 165430.0,
      "text": "that this is a shitty way to improve your English."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165430.0,
      "end_time": 168421.0,
      "text": "Mastering a language is simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168421.0,
      "end_time": 171004.0,
      "text": "It's not easy, to be sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 171004.0,
      "end_time": 174039.0,
      "text": "but it's definitely not complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174039.0,
      "end_time": 177218.0,
      "text": "Learn the language, get a source"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177218.0,
      "end_time": 179801.0,
      "text": "of good language to learn from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 181458.0,
      "end_time": 183537.0,
      "text": "learn the language that you need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 183537.0,
      "end_time": 187084.0,
      "text": "practise it, make it easy to use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 187084.0,
      "end_time": 191087.0,
      "text": "automatic, fluent, and then just do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 191087.0,
      "end_time": 193272.0,
      "text": "It really is that simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 193272.0,
      "end_time": 197087.0,
      "text": "But, you need to be doing it every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 197087.0,
      "end_time": 201212.0,
      "text": "You need to be learning new language every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 201212.0,
      "end_time": 203783.0,
      "text": "Practising on a regular basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 203783.0,
      "end_time": 207100.0,
      "text": "Getting out there, doing more with your English."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 207100.0,
      "end_time": 209426.0,
      "text": "You can't do nothing in English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 209426.0,
      "end_time": 210854.0,
      "text": "and then expect to get better."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210854.0,
      "end_time": 212470.0,
      "text": "It's not gonna happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 212470.0,
      "end_time": 214480.0,
      "text": "Again, kind of obvious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 214480.0,
      "end_time": 217655.0,
      "text": "but something that many people overlook."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217655.0,
      "end_time": 221312.0,
      "text": "Of course, if you're not too sure what language to learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 221312.0,
      "end_time": 222940.0,
      "text": "how to practise it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 222940.0,
      "end_time": 225500.0,
      "text": "or really how to do any of what I've just said."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 225500.0,
      "end_time": 227875.0,
      "text": "If you're confused about the whole"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 227875.0,
      "end_time": 231647.0,
      "text": "English-improvement process, check out my book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 231647.0,
      "end_time": 234951.0,
      "text": "Master English Fast, An Uncommon Guide"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 234951.0,
      "end_time": 237526.0,
      "text": "to Speaking Extraordinary English."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 237526.0,
      "end_time": 240862.0,
      "text": "It'll show you step by step the whole process."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 240862.0,
      "end_time": 243804.0,
      "text": "It'll walk you through improving your English"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243804.0,
      "end_time": 246519.0,
      "text": "as an intermediate to advanced English learner."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 246519.0,
      "end_time": 249965.0,
      "text": "Now, I said there were two things"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 249965.0,
      "end_time": 253532.0,
      "text": "that are very important, and there are."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253532.0,
      "end_time": 256115.0,
      "text": "If you are struggling to speak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 257072.0,
      "end_time": 258895.0,
      "text": "if you're hesitating in conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 258894.99999999997,
      "end_time": 260730.99999999997,
      "text": "'cause you don't know the language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 260731.0,
      "end_time": 263127.0,
      "text": "go back to the first point, what I just talked about."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 263127.0,
      "end_time": 266865.0,
      "text": "But if you are still finding it difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 266865.0,
      "end_time": 269911.0,
      "text": "what you've gotta ask yourself is why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 269911.0,
      "end_time": 271610.0,
      "text": "Why are you hesitating?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 271610.0,
      "end_time": 273346.0,
      "text": "Is it that you don't know the words?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 273346.0,
      "end_time": 274795.0,
      "text": "Is it that you don't know the phrases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 274795.0,
      "end_time": 279056.0,
      "text": "the chunks that you need to communicate with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 279056.0,
      "end_time": 282706.0,
      "text": "Or, is it that you have no idea what to say?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 282706.0,
      "end_time": 286122.0,
      "text": "Many people say, my mind went blank."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 286122.0,
      "end_time": 289645.0,
      "text": "I drew blanks, I didn't know what to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 289645.0,
      "end_time": 293321.0,
      "text": "Is it because you don't have anything interesting to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 293321.0,
      "end_time": 295710.0,
      "text": "no content in here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 295710.0,
      "end_time": 299590.0,
      "text": "Because this is also an important part of speaking English."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 299590.0,
      "end_time": 302117.0,
      "text": "You need three things to speak English well."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 302117.0,
      "end_time": 305583.0,
      "text": "Of course, you need the language, that much is obvious."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 305583.0,
      "end_time": 308187.0,
      "text": "If you don't have the phrases and the expressions"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 308187.0,
      "end_time": 310478.0,
      "text": "that you need to express the things"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 310478.0,
      "end_time": 312477.0,
      "text": "that you want to express,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 312477.0,
      "end_time": 314226.0,
      "text": "you're not gonna be able to say anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 314226.0,
      "end_time": 315965.0,
      "text": "that you want to say in English."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 315965.0,
      "end_time": 318633.0,
      "text": "But, you also need an understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 318633.0,
      "end_time": 320520.0,
      "text": "of the things that you're talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 320520.0,
      "end_time": 323737.0,
      "text": "Background knowledge, content."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 323737.0,
      "end_time": 326344.0,
      "text": "If you are not speaking well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 326344.0,
      "end_time": 328810.0,
      "text": "or hesitating because you've got nothing to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 328810.0,
      "end_time": 331291.0,
      "text": "well, you need to get out more."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 331291.0,
      "end_time": 334831.0,
      "text": "Do more things in English, or in your native language."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 334831.0,
      "end_time": 338849.0,
      "text": "Because often when people have this problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 338849.0,
      "end_time": 340405.0,
      "text": "and I'm sorry to say this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 340405.0,
      "end_time": 342003.0,
      "text": "but often I'll talk to people and they'll say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 342003.0,
      "end_time": 344258.0,
      "text": "well I don't speak English very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 344258.0,
      "end_time": 345739.0,
      "text": "But actually, no, they don't speak their own"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 345739.0,
      "end_time": 347981.0,
      "text": "native language very well either."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 347981.0,
      "end_time": 350213.0,
      "text": "Because they're boring in both languages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 350213.0,
      "end_time": 351424.0,
      "text": "and that's the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 351424.0,
      "end_time": 354351.0,
      "text": "Get out there more, have more experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 354351.0,
      "end_time": 357176.0,
      "text": "Do more things, have more stories to tell."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 357176.0,
      "end_time": 358968.0,
      "text": "Of course, you need the language"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 358968.0,
      "end_time": 360830.0,
      "text": "in order to tell those stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 360830.0,
      "end_time": 362892.0,
      "text": "to talk about those experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 362892.0,
      "end_time": 365605.0,
      "text": "but you also need the actual experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 365605.0,
      "end_time": 368658.0,
      "text": "You need both of these things to speak well."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 368658.0,
      "end_time": 372325.0,
      "text": "And only when you have both of these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 373529.0,
      "end_time": 376314.0,
      "text": "as well as the third thing, culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 376314.0,
      "end_time": 379525.0,
      "text": "Culture is an understanding of the way that people think."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 379525.0,
      "end_time": 382784.0,
      "text": "Because by definition, when you are speaking in English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 382784.0,
      "end_time": 386629.0,
      "text": "you are talking to people with a different culture to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 386629.0,
      "end_time": 388849.0,
      "text": "Meaning the way they think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 388849.0,
      "end_time": 390015.0,
      "text": "and the way that they communicate"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 390015.0,
      "end_time": 391801.0,
      "text": "is gonna be different to you."
